1 resu lt of the improvement shall be assessed for that year based on
2 the fair cash value as set forth in Section 8 of Article X of this
3 Constitution. The provisions of this section shall not apply to any
4 personal property which may be taxed ad valorem or any property
5 which may be valued or assessed by the State Board of Equalization.
6 The Legislature shall enact any laws necessary to implement the
7 provisions of this section.
