7 B. If any improvements are made to the property, the fair cash
8 value of the improvements shall be assessed in accordance with law
9 by the county assessor and added to the assessed value of the
10 property. Once the fair cash value of the improvements has been
11 added to the fair cash value of the property, the total fair cash
